author: Rory Jones
title: Palestinians Protest on Heels of Israelâ€™s 70th Birthday
text:
Palestinian protesters clashed with the Israeli military at the fence separating the Gaza Strip from Israel on Friday, calling for the right of refugees to return to what is now Israel a day after Israelis celebrated the 70th birthday of their nation.

Four Palestinians died and nearly 100 were injured from Israeli gunfire by early evening, Palestinian health authorities said. The Israeli army earlier Friday said it was on high alert and warned Palestinians via airdropped leaflets to refrain from violence and avoid approaching...
